documentation:
Expose a data object

Args:
    data: The data has the following format
        {
            "type": "counter",
            "name": "app_orders",
            "help": "the amount of orders.",
            "method": "inc",
            "value": 1,
            "labels": {
                "type": "trousers"
            }
        }

Prometheus Counter

Args:
    item: The metric data
        {
            "type": "counter",
            "name": "app_orders",
            "help": "the amount of orders.",
            "method": "inc",
            "value": 1,
            "labels": {
                "type": "trousers"
            }
        }

Prometheus Gauge

Args:
    item: The metric data
        {
            "type": "gauge",
            "name": "app_orders",
            "help": "the amount of orders.",
            "method": "inc", # inc or dec or set
            "value": 1,
            "labels": {
                "type": "trousers"
            }
        }

Prometheus Summary

Args:
    item: The metric data
        {
            "type": "summary",
            "name": "app_orders",
            "help": "the amount of orders.",
            "method": "observe",
            "value": 1,
            "labels": {
                "type": "trousers"
            }
        }

Prometheus Histogram

Args:
    item: The metric data
        {
            "type": "histogram",
            "name": "app_orders",
            "help": "the amount of orders.",
            "method": "observe",
            "value": 1,
            "labels": {
                "type": "trousers"
            }
        }

Prometheus Info

Args:
    item: The metric data
        {
            "type": "info",
            "name": "app_orders",
            "help": "the amount of orders.",
            "value": {'version': '1.2.3', 'buildhost': 'foo@bar'}
        }
